# Agra CA-AI Backend

This is the backend server for the **Agra Chartered Accountant AI System**.

It connects to:
- **ChatGPT (OpenAI)**
- **Gemini (Google)**
- **Perplexity (Sonar Model)**

and returns combined CA-specific output for:
- Financial Statements  
- CMA Data  
- GST/Income Tax Replies  
- Notices  
- Financial Analysis  
- Excel/TB Parsing  

